  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2506390/extras/04934cd23a091bee040e70bbcb82c986.avif?t=1733756504\" width=616 height=170 /></span>Dive into the immersive world of <strong>'Chester The Chest'</strong>.Embrace the captivating atmosphere and breathtaking scenery as you guide Chester on his journey.Traverse through meticulously crafted levels, utilizing mechanics such as walking, jumping, and platforming.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2506390/extras/1a96e748a00fd90f8e027f861ea73cb6.poster.avif?t=1733756504\" width=616 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2506390/extras/1a96e748a00fd90f8e027f861ea73cb6.webm?t=1733756504\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will need to explore and help find lost items while traversing exciting levels filled with secrets and challenges. Explore different places and locate all of Chester's lost objects as you aid the world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2506390/extras/00c596434317a6f02a95ad300c9a4236.avif?t=1733756504\" width=616 height=170 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>Explore and find lost objects</strong></u> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2506390/extras/593d5efe86f6b26c1eba78caef4da230.poster.avif?t=1733756504\" width=616 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2506390/extras/593d5efe86f6b26c1eba78caef4da230.webm?t=1733756504\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>Delve into hidden corners and mysterious terrains, searching for treasures forgotten by time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>Overcome obstacles and traps</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2506390/extras/dcb2865116e4d179a516c6e77a4bd30a.poster.avif?t=1733756504\" width=616 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2506390/extras/dcb2865116e4d179a516c6e77a4bd30a.webm?t=1733756504\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>Test your skills against cunning challenges, evading snares and outsmarting the dangers that lurk.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>Find all magical objects and discover their powers</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2506390/extras/e396e68531466598cb412e221a55b8a7.poster.avif?t=1733756504\" width=616 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2506390/extras/e396e68531466598cb412e221a55b8a7.webm?t=1733756504\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>Embark on a quest to find enchanted relics, unlocking secrets and channeling their mystical energy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>Explore and overcome every single biome</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2506390/extras/56d194edc5f5e5731f6a11c72bc5a5b7.poster.avif?t=1733756504\" width=616 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2506390/extras/56d194edc5f5e5731f6a11c72bc5a5b7.webm?t=1733756504\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>From warm islands to dangerous dungeons, master the unique challenges and beauty of each diverse landscape.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2506390/extras/04934cd23a091bee040e70bbcb82c986.avif?t=1733756504\" width=616 height=170 /></span>Dive into the immersive world of <strong>'Chester The Chest'</strong>.Embrace the captivating atmosphere and breathtaking scenery as you guide Chester on his journey.Traverse through meticulously crafted levels, utilizing mechanics such as walking, jumping, and platforming.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2506390/extras/1a96e748a00fd90f8e027f861ea73cb6.poster.avif?t=1733756504\" width=616 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2506390/extras/1a96e748a00fd90f8e027f861ea73cb6.webm?t=1733756504\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will need to explore and help find lost items while traversing exciting levels filled with secrets and challenges. Explore different places and locate all of Chester's lost objects as you aid the world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2506390/extras/00c596434317a6f02a95ad300c9a4236.avif?t=1733756504\" width=616 height=170 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>Explore and find lost objects</strong></u> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2506390/extras/593d5efe86f6b26c1eba78caef4da230.poster.avif?t=173375650