inline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2506390/extras/56d194edc5f5e5731f6a11c72bc5a5b7.poster.avif?t=1733756504\" width=616 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2506390/extras/56d194edc5f5e5731f6a11c72bc5a5b7.webm?t=1733756504\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>From warm islands to dangerous dungeons, master the unique challenges and beauty of each diverse landscape.</p>",
